                " 1.520+-0.018  0.988+-0.018  1.334+-0.016",
                "See Table 1 for Systems used.",
                ". Where",
                "F(i/j)=(Ci/Cj lattice spect.)/(Ci/Cj thermal spect.),",
                "Ci- fission chamber count rate for i= U233,U235,Pu239.",
                ".Reaction rates ratio uncertainty includes",
                "counting statistics,",
                "uncertainty of correction,",
                "inaccuracies in locating the fission chambers"
